text: Roosevelt Ross Barbour (September 15, 1901 - April 29, 1993) was a Canadian politician. He represented the electoral district of Bonavista South in the Newfoundland and Labrador House of Assembly from 1959 to 1971. He was a member of the Liberal Party of Newfoundland and Labrador.Encyclopedia of Newfoundland and LabradorBorn in Newtown, Newfoundland and Labrador, he was a salesman. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Liberal Party of Newfoundland and Labrador MHAs
